      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:49:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多称特朗普通话后推迟 30 天征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trudeau-says-trump-tariffs-delayed-30-days-after-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多周一与总统唐纳德·特朗普通话后表示，将暂停对加拿大和美国商品征收新关税 30 天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trudeau-says-trump-tariffs-delayed-30-days-after-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 21:42:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大人对特朗普的威胁感到愤怒，嘘美国国歌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-canada-tariffs-stir-up-anger-in-a-mild-mannered-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从纽芬兰的岩石海岸到不列颠哥伦比亚省的高耸森林，加拿大人的内心正在滋生一种陌生的感觉：他们很愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-canada-tariffs-stir-up-anger-in-a-mild-mannered-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 19:13:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克在债务违约风险辩论中采取的举措</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/musk-s-moves-on-treasury-risks-a-debate-over-us-payments-default</link>
      <description><![CDATA[除美国财政部在等待国会提高债务上限的同时现金储备减少的情况外，债券市场参与者通常不会太关注该部门的支付处理部门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/musk-s-moves-on-treasury-risks-a-debate-over-us-payments-default</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 18:35:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普签署行政命令创建主权财富基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-signs-action-to-create-sovereign-wealth-fund-in-next-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普签署了一项行政命令，他表示将指示官员为美国设立主权财富基金，以落实他在总统竞选期间提出的想法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/trump-signs-action-to-create-sovereign-wealth-fund-in-next-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 17:54:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称美国国际开发署需要接管以实现外交政策目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-says-he-s-now-in-charge-of-usaid-as-relief-agency-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国务卿马尔科·卢比奥表示，他目前负责美国国际开发署，并警告美国国会议员，该机构在经过运营审查后可能会被废除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/rubio-says-he-s-now-in-charge-of-usaid-as-relief-agency-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 17:33:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西挑战马斯克并获胜。现在卢拉正在与欧洲分享经验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/brazil-took-on-musk-and-won-now-lula-is-sharing-notes-with-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受到伊隆·马斯克政治攻击的欧洲各国政府正在与其他攻击目标交换意见，而这些攻击目标都非常熟悉特斯拉 X 所有者的手段。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/brazil-took-on-musk-and-won-now-lula-is-sharing-notes-with-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
